name: Purolator 727-200F Takeoff from Calgary
description:
Another classic 727 video for you guys! 
My 80th video from YYC :D
Here's a Purolator (Kelowna Flightcraft) Boeing 727-200F departing Calgary International Airport. Love that smoke trail! Pretty early rotation, too. Hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
